{"data":[{"date":"21:52 25/07","title":"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/bui-tien-dung-phoi-bay-nhieu-van-de-sau-tran-thua-cua-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SLNA chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/7.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00fap QG gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng khi anh li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 18 v\u00e0 22, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng sau nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh Jemie Dwayne v\u00e0 Olaha\u00a0. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 87, Jemie Dwayne m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/photo1532520078312-15325200783121187103518.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9\u00a0nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u00edt d\u1ea7n \u0111i. Trong khi v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cm\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb l\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o 3 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1997 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, ra v\u00e0o thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p l\u00ed v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. \u1ede b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n, ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng ra \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf b\u00e0n thua cu\u1ed1i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m b\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn Jermie Lynch\u00a0c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u00ecn \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/that-thu-tren-san-nha-thay-cua-bui-tien-dung-noi-gi-168-192021.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/that-thu-tren-san-nha-thay-cua-bui-tien-dung-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/that-thu-tren-san-nha-thay-cua-bui-tien-dung-noi-gi-168-192021.html\">Th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<b><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; color: rgb(76, 73, 71); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4643","checkdouble":"192028"},{"date":"22:01 25/07","title":"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-giai-thich-su-ky-gio-giua-ha-noi-va-binh-duong.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f3 l\u00fac b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 1-3 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam khi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Oseni, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tho\u00e1t thua v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_0887.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 khi\u1ebfn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: &quot;Do s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 gi\u1eefa hai c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ganh \u0111ua. B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t, V\u0103n V\u0169 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u00f2n Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n qua h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng l\u00ean th\u00ec H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft, c\u00f2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i U23 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem yeu lon nhat cua Do Hung Dung la luon lam nen cho nguoi khac.\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_0996.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;V\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu, lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn&quot; - V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;T\u01b0 duy chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ee7a D\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha D\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9i chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 90% m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 gi\u1eefa B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 17h00 ng\u00e0y 5/9.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/gay-kho-khan-cho-ha-noi-hlv-tran-minh-chien-giau-bai-291-192025.html\">G\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-ban-ket-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018-372-191996.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (KT): L\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tho\u00e1t thua, CLB Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-20-vleague-su-vo-doi-cua-ha-noi-168-191828.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ha-noi-tuyen-bo-tu-tin-sau-tran-thang-thanh-hoa-168-191784.html\">HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-phai-thua-nhan-mot-su-that-168-191753.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/thanh-hoa-vs-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191730.html\">Thanh H\u00f3a 2-3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4642","checkdouble":"192030"},{"date":"23:16 25/07","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23+3, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn: &ldquo;Theo t\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u01b0\u1edbc trong khu v\u1ef1c h\u1ecd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i. H\u1ecd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd h\u01a1n, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u0129 h\u01a1n, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i hay l\u00e0 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa. N\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta gi\u1edd \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u00ec c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t r\u00f5. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ch\u00fang ta, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd m\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft th\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u \u00c1&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\">ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cao. B\u1ea5t k\u00ec sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. B\u1edfi th\u1ebf t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u00ec r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa th\u00ec t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea5u di\u1ebfm n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3&rdquo;, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed9c chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed l\u1eeda quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m tra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4641","checkdouble":"192032"},{"date":"23:35 25/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-yeu-cau-sao-u23-viet-nam-giam-can.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m PVF, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ra ch\u1ec9 th\u1ecb y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c r\u01b0\u1edbn.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-yeu-cau-Ha-Duc-Chinh-giam-can-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o d\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. \u1ea2nh: Webthethao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 25/7, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. \u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, do ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u00f3m c\u1ef1 li ng\u1eafn v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o m\u01b0a l\u00f3t ph\u00eda trong khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee1 th\u1eeba nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 c\u00e2n theo nh\u01b0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 th\u1ea7y Park y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n trong th\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 qu\u00e3ng ng\u1eafn t\u1ed1t. Do v\u1eady, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o trung tu\u1ea7n th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\">ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4640","checkdouble":"192033"},{"date":"23:56 25/07","title":"Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/quang-hai-doi-mua-chien-dau-truoc-ngay-hoi-quan-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110