  <tr>\r\n            <td>Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c fan nh\u00ed v\u00e2y quanh xin ch\u1eef k\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Quang H\u1ea3i:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-quang-nam-vs-ha-noi-17h00-ngay-96-vleague-2018-372-188119.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 0-1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vuot-sieu-pham-cua-cong-phuong-quang-hai-dan-dau-danh-sach-ban-thang-dep-vong-11-168-187799.html\">T\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m C\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng tuy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00f2ng 11</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ha-noi-vs-khanh-hoa-19h00-ngay-36-vleague-2018-372-187654.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 4-0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (KT): Quang H\u1ea3i s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, \u0111\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng to</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/quang-hai-chan-thuong-ha-noi-gap-kho-truoc-chuyen-lam-khach-slna-291-187231.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch SLNA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-tien-dung-hai-con-nguoi-mot-so-phan-167-187066.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i &ndash; Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng: Hai con ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-khien-quang-hai-sa-sut-tai-vleague-2018-291-187014.html\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Quang H\u1ea3i sa s\u00fat t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4639","checkdouble":"192034"},{"date":"05:24 26/07","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: H\u00e0ng hot Golovin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monaco \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Golovin c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Nga. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea-172-191470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin</span>, Juventus, M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga, song Monaco m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Monaco, anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 6.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Golovin ch\u1ecdn Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c thay v\u00ec Chelsea ho\u1eb7c Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin la cau thu choi hay nhat ben phia Nga khi ghi 1 ban va kien tao 2 ban khac\" title=\"Golovin l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Nga khi ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 2 b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMonaco v\u00e0 CSKA \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Golovin. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, song \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u1edf Monaco kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Chelsea. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Stamford Bridge, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4638","checkdouble":"192035"},{"date":"20:07 25/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 25/7: M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-256-mu-tiep-can-nha-a-quan-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, HLV Conte s\u1eafp t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t, Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 25/6</h2><br>\r\n<h2>M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Rebic<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sport Bild\u00a0ti\u1ebfng \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n CLB Man United \u0111ang h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic t\u1eeb CLB Eintracht Frankfurt. Rebic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i. C\u0169ng theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Rebic, M.U s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 66 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 257 MU ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 257 MU ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-256-mu-tiep-can-nha-a-quan-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Rebic\u00a0\u00a0t\u1eeb CLB Eintracht Frankfurt</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea, Liverpool hay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n M.U trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 6 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u00e3y xem Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e2u thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Marouane Fellaini, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Phil Jones, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<h2>HLV Conte s\u1eafp t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Conte b\u1ecb CLB Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u00ecnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Corriere dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Antonio Conte l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Milan trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5n h\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Conte, Milan c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u00e0 \u00f4ng\u00a0Ivan Gazidis.</p>\r\n<h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes lo M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1eafng tay<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man Utd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford Paul Scholes nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh M.U kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf Champions League b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Sevilla. H\u1ecd thua cu\u1ed9c \u1edf chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec c\u1ea3\u201d, Paul Scholes n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n<h2>Barca s\u1eafp chia tay hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, CLB Barcelona nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Yerry Mina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Digne kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Jordi Alba. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Everton trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 19 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Yerry Mina c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo s\u00e1t sau k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia. Trung v\u1ec7 ghi ba b\u00e0n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 qua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 Lyon l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Arsenal \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ozil sau scandal b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c do b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Mesut \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf Arsenal. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \", HLV Unai Emery cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ozil \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 William</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Mourinho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a Willian v\u1ec1 Chelsea t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 8/2013. \u00d4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-sang-257-cristiano-ronaldo-khoe-hon-ca-cau-thu-20-tuoi-184-191962.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xem th\u00eam: \u0110I\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 25/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m \u00a0tra y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4637","checkdouble":"192016"},{"date":"02:00 26/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Juventus 2-0 Bayern Munich (H1): C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a \"Vieri m\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/juventus-vs-bayern-munich-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Juventus vs Bayern Munich: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Bayern gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 06h00 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH RA S\u00c2N<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div><strong>Juventus (4-3-3):</strong> Mattia Perin; Mattia De Sciglio, Daniele Rugani, Giorgio Chiellini, Alex Sandro; Claudio Marchisio, Miralem Pjanic, Emre Can; Joao Cancelo, Andrea Favilli, Federico Bernardeschi.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Bayern Munich (4-5-1): </strong>Sven Ulreich, Ryan Johansson, Javi Martinez, Josip Stanisic, Juan Bernat; Serge Gnabry, Marcel Zylla, Paul Will, Meritan Shabani, Franck Ribery; Sandro Wagner.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Do \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 n\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi ICC&nbsp;208 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Tuy v\u1eady, \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y, trong khi Bayern \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb (ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ulreich, hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Javi Martinez vs Bernat, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ribery c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wagner) th\u00ec Juventus tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u &quot;h\u00e0ng x\u1ecbn&quot; c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Pjanic, Alex Sandro, Chiellini, De Sciglio. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb kh\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 Andrea Favilli. Hai t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 Joao Cancelo (t\u1eeb Valencia, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan theo di\u1ec7n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n) v\u00e0 Emre Can (t\u1eeb Liverpool) c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 3: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u1edbi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Andrea Favilli - ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 FIFA&nbsp;U20 World Cup 2017 m\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a U20 Vi\u1ec7t nam - nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n&nbsp; Ulreich \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng ra ngo\u00e0i.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-03.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 7: KH\u00d4NG V\u00c0O!! Ribery c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Bayern v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i bu\u1ed9c Perin \u0111\u1ea9y ra!\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-07.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 12: D\u00f9 thua k\u00e9m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 song&nbsp;Bayern m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 16: S\u00daT PH\u1ea0T NGUY HI\u1ec2M. </strong>T\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 v\u00e0 ch\u1ebfch v\u1ec1 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i theo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pjanic tung ra c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 uy l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ulreich.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-16.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 22: D\u00f9 Juventus x\u1ecbn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u01a1i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m m\u1ed9t &quot;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&quot; x\u1ee9 Bavaria h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 26: NGUY HI\u1ec2M.</strong> Serge Gnabry, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal, c\u00f3 pha x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u0103ng song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Perin \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-26.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 27: JUVENTUS TR\u1ea2 L\u1edcI. </strong>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A &quot;tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng&quot; sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 Alex Sandro \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ulreich ph\u1ea3i ra tay.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-27.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 32: JUVENTUS \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C &quot;T\u1eb6NG&quot; B\u00c0N TH\u1eaeNG.</strong> H\u1ebft h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m Ulreich m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, b\u1ecb Marchisio \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i c\u0103ng ngang cho Favalli d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-32.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 40: JUVENTUS N\u00c2NG T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0 L\u00caN 2-0.</strong> Andrea Favilli, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh &quot;Vieri m\u1edbi&quot; b\u1edfi c\u0169ng thu\u1eadn ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 mang phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 l\u1eefng l\u1eaby m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Serie A (t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus, Inter Milan, Atletico Madrid), \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ulreich.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Juventus-phut-40.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 44: Juventus thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 17 tu\u1ed5i Nicolo Fagioli v\u00e0o thay Emre Can, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Liverpool theo di\u1ec7n&nbsp;CNTD v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u00e0o m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 d\u00e0nh cho Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng hay h\u01a1n song l\u1ea1i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</h2>\r\nJuventus: V\u1eafng Ronaldo, Dybala, Higuain, Cuadrado, Mandzukic, Costa, Matuidi, Benatia, Szczesny, Khedira (ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup),&nbsp; Spinazzola, Kastanos (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\nBayern: V\u1eafng Neuer, Boateng, M\u00fcller, Hummels, Kimmich, Goretzka, James Rodriguez, Tolisso, S\u00fcle, Thiago, Lewandowski, Rudy (ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup).<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Juventus vs Bayern Munich tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Juventus vs Bayern Munich tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Juventus-vs-Bayern-Munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus vs Bayern Munich</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\n3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n17/18 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Bayern, 9/12 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 6/8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. Tin tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u01a1n m\u01b0a g\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nJuventus: Perin; Chiellini Sandro, Barzagli, Cancelo; Emre Can, Marchisio, Sturaro, De Sciglio; Pjanic, Bernardeschi.<br>\r\nBayern Munich: Ulreich &ndash; Rafinha, Stanisic, Martinez, Bernat - Will, Sanches, Batista-Meier&nbsp; - Robben, Wagner, Ribery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/21/Highlight-Bayern-Munich-vs-PSG.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4636","checkdouble":"192020"},{"date":"05:00 26/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Tottenham vs Roma 09h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/tottenham-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs Roma: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs AS Roma gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 09h00 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin</h2>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u00e3 thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 8 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br />\r\nRoma th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br />\r\n7/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Roma v\u00e0 6/10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Tottenham k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs Roma ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 267 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs Roma ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 267 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-roma-vs-tottenham-09h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Roma vs Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nT\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n<br />\r\nD\u00f9 2 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa Tottenham v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 tr\u00ean 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung song cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Roma ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9a Tottenham. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3 Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 tr\u00ean t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tottenham g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Son Heung-min, Christian Eriksen v\u00e0 Davinson Sanchez.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4635","checkdouble":"192023"},{"date":"06:01 26/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MU vs AC Milan 10h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs AC Milan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Manchester United vs AC Milan gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 10h00 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n- MU kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ICC 2018.<br>\r\n- Milan v\u1eeba th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Novara (2-0).<br>\r\n- MU \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Milan 3/4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- MU lu\u00f4n ghi t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan.<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Milan t\u1ea1i ICC 2018.<br>\r\n- Milan th\u1eafng k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 5 trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- Man United thua k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n- 6 trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb.<br>\r\n- 4 trong 6 hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1edbi rung.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs AC Milan tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 10h s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m nay 267 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs AC Milan tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 10h s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m nay 267 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-ac-milan-10h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">MU vs AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa Milan v\u00e0 Man United \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean. 4 trong 6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Milan c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-1 Club America </strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/20/MU-1-1-Club-America.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4634","checkdouble":"192027"},{"date":"18:11 25/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/lyon-muon-mua-yerry-mina-cua-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lyon mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean-Michel Aulas c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Yerry Mina tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u201cm\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot\u201d tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n sau 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi Anh song Mina v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Premier League nh\u01b0 Man United, Tottenham v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Everton \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao t\u1edbi 1m95 v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lyon mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lyon mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Lyon-muon-mua-Yerry-Mina-cua-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Mina quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i Barca. Tuy nhi\u00ean, CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a anh th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi b\u1ecf 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadu Clement Lenglet v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u00e0 Mina ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 5 cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 khi Barca v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Gerard Pique, Samuel Umtiti v\u00e0 Thomas Vermaelen.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Lyon nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean-Michel Aulas c\u1ee7a Lyon \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Lyon mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. \u201cTrong \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i \u0111ang m\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0nh Mina v\u1edbi Everton\u201d, Aulas n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu Lyon vs Huddersfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" title=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/lyon-muon-mua-yerry-mina-cua-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lyon mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 doanh thu. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u00edch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Champions League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Barca, Mina ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb Palmeiras \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u1ebfn Lyon, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Champions League khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 Ligue 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f2n Everton, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 8 Premier League, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 Europa League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-vu-malcom-toi-barca-180-191986.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau v\u1ee5 Malcom t\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-nhung-tro-lo-va-so-thich-chuyen-nhuong-cua-barca-180-191984.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Nh\u1eefng tr\u00f2 l\u1ed1 v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-phat-bieu-sau-khi-gia-nhap-barca-180-191961.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Brazil n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1edbi Barca th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4633","checkdouble":"192012"},{"date":"20:34 25/07","title":"CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/clb-real-madrid-dua-ra-gia-ban-tien-ve-tony-kroos.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh.</h2><h2>CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0Toni\u00a0Kroos\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/11/CLB-Real-Madrid-dua-ra-gia-ban-tien-ve-Toni-Kroos--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Toni Kroos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 ngay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 danh hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 29 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m sau. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ea5p ngh\u00e9 tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m, CLB Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n trong vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Kroos \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec l\u00ed do \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chia tay Kroos nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Casillas, Pepe hay v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Ronaldo. Song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Bayern v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022 c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 500 tri\u1ec7u euro..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) thay v\u00ec con s\u1ed1 500 tri\u1ec7u euro (445 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) trong \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia TBN. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB M.U hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro (71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n t\u00f9y v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Kroos. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Michael Carrick v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<em><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#111000;background:#fbfbfb\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></em></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4632","checkdouble":"192017"},{"date":"20:47 25/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn La Liga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Atletico Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Gelson Martins t\u1eeb CLB Sporting Lisbon.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0</span>Gelson Martins</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Gelson Martins c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Gelson Martins c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Gelson Martins \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Gelson Martins, CLB Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y sau b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Sporting Lisbon.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gelson Martins n\u0103m nay 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u0110N n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ho\u1eb7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Sporting Lisbon, Gelson Martins \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 125 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 25 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o trong c\u00e1ch t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 30 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i \u0110TQG, Gelson Martins c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 19 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0u b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Fernando Santos. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Sporting t\u1eebng c\u00e0i v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Gelson \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Gelson Martins \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4n ngoan c\u1ee7a HLV Diego Simeone. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gelson Martins t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi?</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-atletico-dai-chien-vi-vida-172-191350.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/liverpool-va-atletico-dai-chien-vi-vida.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-atletico-dai-chien-vi-vida-172-191350.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Atletico \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Giroud \u201cgi\u00fap\u201d Chelsea</span><br>\r\nAtletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft ph\u00eda Chelsea c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4631","checkdouble":"192018"}]}